345
00:17:43,834 --> 00:17:44,750
I guess that's enough.

346
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:46,240
So it's 6 and a half.

347
00:17:46,240 --> 00:17:50,000
So it's two lab tables
is 13 of these blocks.

348
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,190
All right.

