358
00:18:28,195 --> 00:18:30,300
All right.

359
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,760
I think I worked this out.

360
00:18:42,010 --> 00:18:43,170
So let's see.

361
00:18:43,170 --> 00:18:48,020
That means that N
