371
00:19:37,936 --> 00:19:38,435
Right?

372
00:19:38,435 --> 00:19:42,190
So that's not very
plausible here, all right.

373
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:44,380
So those of you who
voted against this

374
00:19:44,380 --> 00:19:47,080
were actually sort
of half right.

375
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:48,630
And in fact, if you
wanted to get it

376
00:19:48,630 --> 00:19:52,300
to the wall over there,
